summary:
Detailed and results-driven market research and data analysis professional with experience impacting organisational performance through skilled research and analysis. Evaluate market and competitive conditions, current and emerging trends, and industry-specific solutions to ensure information to support organisational objectives. Possess extensive experience of assisting in the development and upgrading of database systems and analytical techniques. 
Exceptional strategist analysing trends and forecasting to develop long-term strategies based on business best practices as well as maximum growth and profitability. Able to play a key role in analysing problems and developing creative solutions as well as producing methodologies and files for effective data management. Fluent in English and Greek.
